Message.SourceString: Watch yourself, cowpoke.
Don't let a yellow-bellied so-and-so stick it to ya.
There's a new sheriff in town... and it's you, pardner!
Now go on, git! I know ya got some quests to finish!
Whooo-ee! It feels good to get some Bars, pardner!
Y'all come back real soon now, ya hear?!
You'll rustle up some big varmints with this here shootin' iron.
Yeehaw! We got a live one!
You're mighty trigger happy for a young gun! I respect it!
Well, get a wiggle on and place yer order!
I got gear that'll really swat yer fireflies!
Let's stop those Bars from burnin' a hole in yer pocket!
How I'd love to hunt fresh chicken! If only I had the fortitude...
You'd never use this on a poor vending machine, would you? Perish the thought!
Go forth with the roguish swagger of a player with a brand new shotgun!
My word, you're the very picture of class with that new shotgun!
Quite the munitions loadout, old sport!
You daren't forget to reload! Your weapon simply will NOT work without ammunition.
Headed out on a hunt, are we?  Positively delightful!
Right-o! Pick your poison!
Oh, jolly good show!
What are we perusing today, hmm?
Let me guess, a shotgun? Oh ho, just a quip!
I have a delightful array of armaments!
Congratulations on diversifying your portfolio.
A brilliant choice for a player of discerning tastes!
Hodl on to it! To the moon!
I wish you many returns on this investment!
You gotta spend Bars to make Bars!
Thanks for the generous Bar infusion.
A wise investment, user!
Might I suggest our most expensive option?
This one will definitely pay dividends.
If you're making a large withdrawal, I may need you to fill out a few forms.
I have options for all budgets: big, and very, very big!
So you're ready to make a deposit!
Don't shoot it all in one place!
You won't regret it.
Now get out there and point that thing at anyone but me.
No scope? YES scope!
Find some high ground and take a deep breath. You'll do great.
Good choice. Now, make it count.
You always know how to hit your mark..
I picked this one out just for you.
I've got the gun of your dreams.
Try this one on for size.
Scope these weapons.
Anything standing out to you?
Here's your secret: those Bars? We eat them like dog kibble. Enjoy the gun!
... oh, you still want a secret? Uhh... Oh no! My circuits! You'll have to try again later.
Look, kid... I'll level with you. There's no secret. But if you ask again... That's on you.
Your secret: I once saw Peely hug an apple he found on the ground for 20 full minutes.
Here's your secret: Spicy Fish are hot because they're angry all the time.
Here's a secret: Meowscles's favorite protein shake flavor is Coconut Stink Flopper.
A-ha! Excellent. I knew you were seeker of knowledge... And of big guns!
You fell for that?! Ahem, I mean, of course. Good secret sharing imminent.
Has anyone ever told you you're a little bit... gullible?
So... You want gear AND a secret?
How about just a secret, for double the Bars?
Hehehe. This was too easy.
